text: Enkelejda Arifi (born 20 May 1974 in Rrogozhinë) is an Albanian folk singer of cham origin. She is the niece of popular folk singer Hysni Alushi. ==References== Category:Albanian female singers Category:People from Rrogozhinë Category:Living people Category:1974 births Category:21st-century women singers
title: Enkelejda Arifi
